title: "NEXAH-CODEX — Navigator 2.2 (Public Edition) + GEOMETRIA NOVA"
abstract: >
  Open research repository for the NEXAH-CODEX, a transdisciplinary framework
  exploring resonance architecture across mathematics, physics, geometry and
  consciousness. This release publishes the Navigator 2.2 (Public Edition)
  and the core module GEOMETRIA NOVA, including systems map, visual navigation
  grid, and public builder interface.
